txt.en: Destroy many dark forges in Búrzangh.
Búrzangh, the Shrouded Forge, can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should destroy the dark forges.
You have destroyed many of the dark forges within Búrzangh. The Rangers of Ithilien will be pleased with your efforts on their behalf.

The Dead are moulded and reforged within the Shrouded Forge of Búrzangh, to serve those in control of Minas Morgul. The dark flames emanating from the forges should be extinguished to halt the work of those in the Shrouded Forge.
